data.description: This is it! Spectacular panoramic mountain and waterfall views on a 1.38 acre fully fenced lot located near scenic Ramsey Canyon Preserve and just minutes from town. Gorgeous and tastefully updated 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with generous 2,603 sq.ft. floor plan, including a bonus room with a separate entrance and attached bathroom that could easily be a 4th bedroom or guest suite. Outdoor living and entertainment options are endless with the lap pool and spa, outdoor kitchen with built-in BBQ, two covered patios, and  additional courtyard and uncovered patio space. Come see this truly special home!
